X-WR-CALNAME:Lioness line disruption
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-05-30T03:30:00&endDate=2026-06-01T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nLIONESS LINE: Saturday 30 and Sunday 31 May\, no service between Euston and Watford Junction. There will also be no BAKERLOO LINE service between Queens Park and Harrow & Wealdstone. A very limited SOUTHERN service will continue to serve Wembley Central early and late on Saturday and on Sunday\, and Watford Junction on Saturday and Sunday\, and LONDON NORTH WESTERN RAILWAY trains stop at Harrow & Wealdstone\, Bushey and Watford Junction. If travelling to Wembley for the Rugby League Challenge Cup Finals\, please use Wembley Park. Special bus services 718 and 720 operate.
DTEND:20260601T002900Z
DTSTART:20260530T033000Z
SUMMARY:Lioness line: Planned Closure
UID:342c5254-0a86-47e1-9b91-cc63c3fc8f99@342c.org
END:VEVENT
